paragraphs.title: 分渠道 top 500 下载次数
paragraphs.text:
val select_channel = z.select("channel", "全部", globalChannel.map(p => (p, p)).toSeq)

val select_channel_value = s"${select_channel}"

var where = " "

if ((!"全部".equalsIgnoreCase(select_channel_value))  && select_channel_value != null && select_channel_value.trim.length != 0 ) {
     where += " where channel = '" +  select_channel_value + "' "
}

val sql = s"  select channel, key , count from  ${channelTopKeyDownloadType}${dayHoursTableSuffix} ${where} "

z.show(sqlContext.sql(sql))

paragraphs.title: 分渠道 top 500 下载流量
paragraphs.text:
val select_channel = z.select("channel", "全部", globalChannel.map(p => (p, p)).toSeq)

val select_channel_value = s"${select_channel}"

var where = " "

if ((!"全部".equalsIgnoreCase(select_channel_value))  && select_channel_value != null && select_channel_value.trim.length != 0 ) {
     where += " where channel = '" +  select_channel_value + "' "
}

val sql = s"  select channel, key , flux from ${channelTopKeyFluxType}${dayHoursTableSuffix} ${where}  "

z.show(sqlContext.sql(sql))
